Despite aggressive messaging by Republicans to paint Pelosi as a villain, the idea of another Pelosi speakership doesn't seem to sway voters one way or the other â€” in a CNN poll out this week , just 34% of registered voters said Pelosi will be an extremely or very important factor in their vote in 2018, putting her at the bottom of their voting considerations.

